

### markdown style

![头像](https://i.loli.net/2019/08/09/j8RkzJ1mNxTswYV.png)

### tex style

\comment: 单行指令
\img: https://i.loli.net/2019/08/09/j8RkzJ1mNxTswYV.png

\comment: 字符指令
\img[https://i.loli.net/2019/08/09/j8RkzJ1mNxTswYV.png][头像]

\comment: 参数指令
\img {"https://i.loli.net/2019/08/09/j8RkzJ1mNxTswYV.png", "头像"}

\comment: 具名参数指令
\img {
    link = "https://i.loli.net/2019/08/09/j8RkzJ1mNxTswYV.png"
    alt = "头像"
}

## single body

### markdown style

```quote{type = "danger"}
这是一条**危险**信息
```

### tex style

\quote: 这是一条普通信息

\quote[这是一条**危险**信息][danger]

\quote {
    type = "danger"
    body = "这是一条**危险**信息"
}


### jsx/vue style

<quote type="danger">
这是一条**危险**信息
</quote>


## Multi bodies

### tex style

\begin{tabs}
    \push{terms}
    纸曲笔伏霍音起
    \push{terms}
    疑似圣驾过丽沟
\end{tabs}


### jsx/vue style

<tabs>
    <terms>
    纸曲笔伏霍音起
    </terms>
    <terms>
    疑似圣驾过丽沟
    </terms>
